---
// SILO — static /go/reserve redirect (R14 GitHub-Pages migration, 2026-07-15).
// Replaces the Netlify go.mts env-indirection with a baked destination. Losing
// swap-provider-without-deploy is accepted; edit DEST below + rebuild to swap.
const DEST = 'https://ontopo.com/he/il/page/silo';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content={`0; url=${DEST}`} />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <link rel="canonical" href={DEST} />
    <title>SILO — מעבר להזמנת מקום</title>
    <script is:inline set:html={`location.replace(${JSON.stringify(DEST)});`}></script>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;background:#fffaed;color:#241813;display:grid;place-items:center;min-height:100vh;margin:0;">
    <p>מעבירים אתכם להזמנת מקום… <a href={DEST}>המשך ידני</a></p>
  </body>
</html>
